[SAY] Done. Look at the bottom of the screen.
[SAY] That green bar is the tmux status bar. On the left, you see zero in brackets — that's your session name.
[SAY] Next to it, zero colon zsh star. Window zero, running zsh. The star means it's the active window.
[SAY] On the right, the current time and date.
[SAY] To leave, just type exit.
[TYPE] 'exit'

